%p#notice= notice

%h1= t('.title_html')
= image_tag("cover.jpg", :style => "height:200px;overflow: hidden;")
- cache @products do
  - @products.each do |product|
    - cache product do
      .entry
        = image_tag(product.image_url)
        %h3= link_to content_tag(:strong, raw(product.name)), product, :title => product.name
        = sanitize(product.description)
        .price_line
          %span.price= number_to_currency(product.price)
          = button_to t('.add_html'),
            cart_products_path(product_id: product, locale: I18n.locale),
            remote: true
